    "h1_count": 5,
    "blockquote": "Unquoting is an insurance company sells property and casualty and health and life insurance to protect you and your assets in Ohio. Unquoting Insurance Company is a state licensed insurance school in that offers pre-licensing education classes in person and live streamed across the state of Ohio. Why Unquoting? Because too often, people are given numbers without explanations. Coverage without context. Protection without clarity. Here, we break insurance down into plain language, so you can make informed decisions without pressure. The team emphasizes education, tailored solutions, prompt customer care, and serving both individuals and businesses.",
